  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the puzzle by dragging the colored tiles to get the perfect gradient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/e61856516a0f72816288d1a32efd7322.poster.avif?t=1741007728\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/e61856516a0f72816288d1a32efd7322.webm?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/e61856516a0f72816288d1a32efd7322.mp4?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has two modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal mode:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty is gradually increasing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try your hand at solving the puzzle in one turn:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/516e4316e178ed170bf5f0a959746b28.poster.avif?t=1741007728\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/516e4316e178ed170bf5f0a959746b28.webm?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/516e4316e178ed170bf5f0a959746b28.mp4?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or put together a puzzle in the given time:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/4f2af4163f428db3baeb6e6ad8dde993.poster.avif?t=1741007728\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/4f2af4163f428db3baeb6e6ad8dde993.webm?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/4f2af4163f428db3baeb6e6ad8dde993.mp4?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sandbox.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize the level generation to suit your mood and play without paying attention to time or the number of moves.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/6075d5757f44767bb70aa7b3dea61aec.poster.avif?t=1741007728\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/6075d5757f44767bb70aa7b3dea61aec.webm?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/6075d5757f44767bb70aa7b3dea61aec.mp4?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve the puzzle by dragging the colored tiles to get the perfect gradient.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/e61856516a0f72816288d1a32efd7322.poster.avif?t=1741007728\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/e61856516a0f72816288d1a32efd7322.webm?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/e61856516a0f72816288d1a32efd7322.mp4?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game has two modes:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Normal mode:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty is gradually increasing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try your hand at solving the puzzle in one turn:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/516e4316e178ed170bf5f0a959746b28.poster.avif?t=1741007728\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/516e4316e178ed170bf5f0a959746b28.webm?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/516e4316e178ed170bf5f0a959746b28.mp4?t=1741007728\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or put together a puzzle in the given time:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3511670/extras/4f2af4163f428db3baeb6e6ad8dd